    <item>
      <title>台湾南部四月最热气温创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/hottest-april-temperatures-on-record-scorch-southern-taiwan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周末台湾南部部分地区气温飙升至历史新高，当局警告周一高温可能持续，并敦促人们避免不必要的户外活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/hottest-april-temperatures-on-record-scorch-southern-taiwan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 04:20:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国锂精炼厂 Ecopro 因电动汽车需求疲软而减产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/korean-lithium-refiner-ecopro-cuts-output-on-weakening-ev-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国金属精炼商 Ecopro Innovation Co. 已将用于电池的氢氧化锂产量比一年前削减 10%，以应对全球电动汽车需求增长疲软的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/korean-lithium-refiner-ecopro-cuts-output-on-weakening-ev-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 03:33:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美国施压出售或禁止应用程序，TikTok 誓言进行法律斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tiktok-vows-legal-battle-as-the-us-presses-for-app-s-sale-or-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 告诉员工，如果美国强制禁止或剥离这款中国应用程序的法案签署成为法律，它将在法庭上进行斗争，因为世界上最有价值的科技企业之一正试图抵御其最重要市场的生存危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tiktok-vows-legal-battle-as-the-us-presses-for-app-s-sale-or-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 03:18:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉降价引发中国新一轮电动车价格战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tesla-s-price-cuts-trigger-new-round-in-china-ev-price-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司周末在中国大幅降价的举动可能会引发中国新一轮激烈的价格战，理想汽车公司立即做出回应，对新车型提供折扣和现金回扣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tesla-s-price-cuts-trigger-new-round-in-china-ev-price-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:48:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>期权交易商表示，台积电的跌幅可能还会进一步扩大 13%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tsmc-s-13-rout-may-have-further-to-go-options-traders-indicate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在芯片制造商的谨慎指引以及对人工智能交易是否正在平仓的担忧之后，台积电的期权交易员正在应对不断上升的看空浪潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tsmc-s-13-rout-may-have-further-to-go-options-traders-indicate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:37:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克在 X 上发布的悉尼袭击图片引发了澳大利亚的愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/australia-flags-fight-with-elon-musk-over-social-media-takedowns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚正准备与埃隆·马斯克和美国社交媒体巨头展开斗争，指控他们在过去 10 天悉尼发生的两起暴力袭击事件中未能足够快地采取行动来监管图形内容和错误信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/australia-flags-fight-with-elon-musk-over-social-media-takedowns</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 01:41:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能明星寻求 2030 年将自动驾驶汽车引入日本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/this-100-million-firm-seeks-self-driving-cars-in-japan-by-2030</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当山本一政的算法击败日本顶级国际象棋棋手时，他成为日本最著名的人工智能开发者之一。现在，他正在追求一项更具挑战性的人体仿真任务：实现完全自动驾驶的汽车系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/this-100-million-firm-seeks-self-driving-cars-in-japan-by-2030</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 为美国“撤资或禁止”法做好准备——和一场法律斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tiktok-braces-for-us-law-requiring-a-sale-and-fresh-legal-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过多年努力向美国政府保证其受欢迎的社交媒体应用程序不会对国家安全构成威胁，TikTok 在这场斗争中的失败现在看来几乎是不可避免的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tiktok-braces-for-us-law-requiring-a-sale-and-fresh-legal-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 00:12:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>竞争对手证实需求不断增长，SK 海力士将掀起人工智能浪潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/sk-hynix-is-set-to-surf-ai-wave-as-rivals-confirm-strength-of-chip-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美光科技公司等公司的稳健盈利巩固了人们对人工智能芯片需求的乐观情绪之后，SK海力士公司在本周发布财报时将不得不应对高预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/sk-hynix-is-set-to-surf-ai-wave-as-rivals-confirm-strength-of-chip-demand</guid>
